            <h3>Project Overview</h3>
            <p>
                This project demonstrates building a <strong>serverless application</strong> using the <strong>AWS Serverless Application Model (SAM)</strong> 
                and automating deployments through a <strong>multi-stage CI/CD pipeline</strong> with <strong>GitHub Actions</strong>.
            </p>
