                <li>Bootstrapped pipeline resources for <strong>Dev</strong> and <strong>Prod</strong> stages using SAM pipeline.</li>
                <li>Configured <strong>GitHub Actions</strong> to automatically build, test, and deploy on every commit.</li>
                <li>Deployed infrastructure via <strong>CloudFormation</strong> stacks managed by SAM.</li>
            </ul>
